OL,3,CReform backs #57m loan to reopen
OL,4,Cairport after 'u-turn'
OL,6,FCouncillors have voted to approve a
OL,7,F#57 million loan to reopen Doncaster
OL,8,FSheffield Airport (DSA) after Reform
OL,9,Fmembers threatened to withdraw their
OL,10,Fsupport for the previously agreed deal.
OL,12,FCity of Doncaster Council voted by a
OL,13,Fmajority last November to rubber-stamp
OL,14,Fa borrowing package which would
OL,15,Fsupport plans to get the site up and
OL,16,Frunning for the first time since 2022.
OL,18,FBut in recent weeks, Reform
OL,19,Fcouncillors said they had backed the
OL,20,Fdecision without being able to
OL,21,Fscrutinise key clauses of the lease.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778526673
OL,3,CReform backs #57m loan to reopen
OL,4,Cairport after 'u-turn'
OL,6,FHowever, at an extraordinary meeting
OL,7,Fof Doncaster Council on Monday, Reform
OL,8,Fagreed to the loan subject to being
OL,9,Fable to see copies of the new lease
OL,10,Fbefore it was approved.
OL,12,FLabour Mayor of Doncaster, Ros Jones,
OL,13,Fdismissed the Reform threat as a
OL,14,F"political stunt".
OL,16,F"They've had all the information there
OL,17,Fand just not read it," she said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778526673
OL,3,CReform backs #57m loan to reopen
OL,4,Cairport after 'u-turn'
OL,6,F"It's delayed work going on for
OL,7,Fnegotiations for two months. It's also
OL,8,Fputting people at fear so we have had
OL,9,Fseveral people rescind their
OL,10,Fapplications which were vital points
OL,11,Fthat we need to make because these
OL,12,Fpeople are needed to reopen the
OL,13,Fairport.
OL,15,F"I'm delighted to see Reform's done
OL,16,Fthe u-turn and know what it's all
OL,17,Fabout.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778526673
OL,3,CReform backs #57m loan to reopen
OL,4,Cairport after 'u-turn'
OL,6,F"This is about Doncaster, it's about
OL,7,FDoncaster Airport and driving forward.
OL,8,FIt's the right economic decision for
OL,9,FDoncaster."
OL,11,FDSA was closed in late 2022, with the
OL,12,Floss of about 800 jobs, after owners
OL,13,FPeel Group said it was no longer
OL,14,Ffinancially viable.
OL,16,FIn addition to the loan, political
OL,17,Fleaders have approved #160m of public
OL,18,Fmoney to revive the airport.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778526673
OL,3,CReform backs #57m loan to reopen
OL,4,Cairport after 'u-turn'
OL,6,FA rally was held outside Doncaster
OL,7,FCivic Hall ahead of Monday's meeting
OL,8,Fin support of the loan deal.
OL,10,FWhile Reform has the highest number of
OL,11,Fseats of any party on the council, the
OL,12,Felected mayor and her cabinet are
OL,13,Fresponsible for most decisions.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Reform UK Doncaster
OL,16,Fsaid it had "sought to deliver tighter
OL,17,Foversight, scrutiny, and governance of
OL,18,Fthe Airport project - conditions that
OL,19,Fthe Labour administration had failed
OL,20,Fto put in place".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778526673
OL,3,CReform backs #57m loan to reopen
OL,4,Cairport after 'u-turn'
OL,6,FLeader Craig Ward said: "The fact
OL,7,Fthese safeguards had to be forced
OL,8,Fthrough by Reform shows this Labour
OL,9,Fadministration has not acted in the
OL,10,Fbest interests of the people of
OL,11,FDoncaster.
OL,13,F"Proper financial accountability,
OL,14,Ftransparency, and scrutiny should have
OL,15,Fbeen there from the very beginning
OL,16,Fwhen dealing with hundreds of millions
OL,17,Fof pounds of public money."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778526673
OL,3,CReform backs #57m loan to reopen
OL,4,Cairport after 'u-turn'
OL,6,FLabour's South Yorkshire Mayor, Oliver
OL,7,FCoppard, said: "We need to back this
OL,8,Fproject. It's a huge amount of
OL,9,Ftaxpayers money, it's a big public
OL,10,Fsector investment project.
OL,12,F"If we want it to succeed, which
OL,13,FReform now say they do, then we need
OL,14,Fto be absolutely be very clear that
OL,15,Fover the long-term this has to have
OL,16,Fall our support.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778526673
OL,3,CReform backs #57m loan to reopen
OL,4,Cairport after 'u-turn'
OL,6,F"I hope we have now got over the final
OL,7,Fhurdle. I hope Reform will continue to
OL,8,Fback this project, now that they
OL,9,Funderstand exactly what the risks and
OL,10,Fthe opportunities look like, and we
OL,11,Fcan all move forward together."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/8
